{"tid":1337661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［交通直擊］721 中環現場","createTime":"2019-07-21T10:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T10:29:44.000Z","uid":88420,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ae3162ba39ca82acad1f419c66993cd8459aaa72","tid":1337661,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:18:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中環交通消息</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">干諾道中畢打街交界 怡和大廈交易廣場對開 簡單路障全面佔領</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n干諾道中大會堂對出 東西行線全面佔領<br />\n遮打道皇后像廣場對開 東西行線封閉 未被佔領 路面佈滿姐姐<br />\n遮打道行人專用區 有零聲遊行人士逗留<br />\n德輔道中 東西行線封閉 遊行人士經過後立即散去<br />\nHarcourt Road 有大量人潮湧往中環<br />\n<br />\n暫時未見警察維持交通秩序<br />\n請大家保持警惕 注意行車安全 慢慢移往中環<br />\n<br />\n18:15 畢打街干諾道中對出<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bB3rRtz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbB3rRtz.png&h=70869590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n17:55 和平紀念碑對出<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYxXdEs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYxXdEs.png&h=108957db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場大量聲音表示 「光復香港 時代革命」<br />\n<br />\n=====<br />\n<br />\n去中環嘅四大原因：<br />\n<br />\n1. 地勢可攻可守<br />\n<br />\n中環有大量會所同酒店，犬隻唔會夠膽亂黎<br />\n萬一有任何問題，出碼頭有多條路，可以經 IFC 怡和大廈 以至上環方向，仲可以走上山腰荷李活道同埋半山向西行<br />\n加上中環站同香港站有大量出口（全港最多 / 第二多）犬隻難以完全封鎖<br />\n<br />\n相反犬隻一早係金鐘佈防 無論如何亦衝唔到入去政總立法會 反而犬隻一封地鐵站同埋太古廣場 好似612咁 就全場被包抄<br />\n<br />\n2. 中環 = 香港核心<br />\n<br />\n萬一今晚會持續到聽日日間<br />\n中環內街同埋寫字樓都會癱瘓<br />\n中環嘅外資同中小企數目絕對比金鐘多<br />\n當初 2014 年佔中都係以中環為目標<br />\n因為咁樣先可以向政權施壓<br />\n<br />\n3. 補給<br />\n<br />\n而且留意中環嘅補給絕對比金鐘好<br />\n上環、半山、以至對面海運補給都方便好多<br />\n金鐘超市賣曬野之後就要靠灣仔中環<br />\n但係犬隻一封金鐘道同 Harcourt （或者愛丁堡廣場對出）就會斷糧<br />\n<br />\n4. 本來遊行就係以中環為終點！<br />\n中環終審法院！<br />\n記得嗎？我地要堅持到底<br />\n<br />\n依家跳過遊行隊伍 去緊中環睇下環境<br />\n如果環境許可 會翻去軍器廠街及社聯對出呼籲大家出中環 大家加油 不撤不散 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e1c5bf5e5c613f9d1c2ce76152f7d428ac7808","tid":1337661,"uid":258055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:19:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f943260eb42af6ca955324a5e50c9abac3b5e93","tid":1337661,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n公民抗命 =&gt; 民族抗命 =&gt; 時代革命"},{"pid":"955e5315a40b77f76be7480ff67edb41999ed805","tid":1337661,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:20:29.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"bc3f3a2f343270dc0ec25cd9ecff900df434e9ca","tid":1337661,"uid":283881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:20:59.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"2545018dc1c6ca7aba714e5cb0ac48fc3eecc47a","tid":1337661,"uid":90452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:23:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"807c28795a59ef39a2ae22dee725394abe5cba38","tid":1337661,"uid":10901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54577d81d8142f767d45438eb1dac86ec2de7b07","tid":1337661,"uid":90452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:24:40.000Z","msg":"真係好對唔住 我依家仲番緊工 收工會即刻出黎 等我 各位手足要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: large;\">帶齊gear以防萬一</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87101d34f8fecfb132f13e4d945df688690ced22","tid":1337661,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:24:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad7bdb643f4db39713421315e043f4e3d3bbab56","tid":1337661,"uid":71081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:24:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"421f9b41529a448d3fa6bd1156b6e64763c42e0e","tid":1337661,"uid":274558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:25:35.000Z","msg":"佔中"},{"pid":"1f1e2c32229a6f7f45c0d8a7a364d7bd06c67641","tid":1337661,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:28:01.000Z","msg":"和平記念碑"},{"pid":"e514b12594d0d354e8f6e5f28e0c3edead0ba580","tid":1337661,"uid":88420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T10:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4oSM4p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4oSM4p.png&h=26d5f04d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遮打道歷山大廈外仍然鬆動<br />\n皇后大道中車輛不能通行<br />\n中環站開始多黑衫出閘"}]}